oth decrease.</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The electric potential at the surface decreases and the charge of Sphere <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span> increases.</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The electric potential at the surface increases and the charge of Sphere <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span> decreases.</p>"],"answer":1}]